Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know forget the identification\Nwith the physical and the mental and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,your name and occupation and all those\Nways of specifying linear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,separateness.\NAnd see yourself as reflecting a a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,reflecting qualities.\NSee yourself as
