Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You act out and be that quality.\NThat's if you reflect that quality then
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to think anymore\Nbecause you just are that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which you are automatically\Ndoes that which is concordant with the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,field.\NSo to be polite and considerate then
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,means that you value that quality and\Nyou become that which you value.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you want people to be considerate\Nand generous and nice to you, then all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to do is reflect that quality.\NSo right away you see, you're out of the
