Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All we want to know about you, we can\Nlook up on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's so paranoid about their\Nprivacy and the government and all. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hysterical.\NDon't worry about your privacy. You
