Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all the the individual the\Nindividual see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's all the linear domain and\Nthat's what people get stuck in. They
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,think that they are all those\Nspecifications.
