Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,very polite. Everybody knocked\Nthemselves out to be as um congenial as
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,possible. We stayed in a lovely place.\NEverybody treated us elegantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We went for a handsome ride in the in\Nthe park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The horses were friendly. Everybody was\Nfriendly. So what is the complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh so\Nyou become the become the quality become
