Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because there isn't really any any\Nentity there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When the entity disappears, that which\Nyou've become continues to walk around
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world, talk and it even gives\Nlectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what it was going to do\Nfor many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea what it was going to do\Nfor many years, much less talk again or
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,write again. No such thing was even\Nimaginable. So then
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,um sharing uh that which you've come to\Nknow by being it uh became
