Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,know what I'm saying?\NSo, Fleming ran around, everybody tried
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to get him interested in uh antibiotics,\Nyou know, penicellin was the onset of
