Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was only because of the infection\Nin the wounds of the soldiers in World
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,War II that the army, I believe it was,\Npaid attention to him. And
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway, you can see if Fleming had the\Nopportunity to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,uh once he's discovered penicellin, he\Ncan't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's the penicellin that's keeping\Nme here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,until I finish this book. Anyway,\Ndo we have uh we have slides today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We do.\N>> We do. Do we have the What's the last
