Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,>> In a computer world, you should be able\Nto go to the end first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NNo, that's not the end.
