Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody in charge here, folks.\NJust think of that. There's nobody in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,charge.\NWell, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's party time. Party time.\NNobody running this place. There's
