Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll fill our pockets. I'll take\Nthe speaker. You take the Uhoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,\Nthat book is going to be out in October
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh\Nhysterical.
