Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,don't get into guruism either.\NThe quality that you wish to own within
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself is already a reality. It only\Nwaits for you to own it. Once you own
