Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The world will reflect back a\Nconfirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to be hateful, the world\Nwill oblige you and hate you. See, then
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you can say how hateful the world is and\Nhate it without feeling guilty about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See?\NSo you envision that which that quality
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which you wish to own because it's\Nalready a reality. So you don't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,create it. You don't have to create it.\NYou don't have to wish for it. You have
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to you can't there's no point chasing it\Nor desiring it. It's just just a quality
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you just be that quality. You\Nreflect that quality which is already
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,present.\NSo if you value then kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,consideration, you'll find yourself\Ngoing through the world being polite,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,saying thank you.\NSaying thank you is fun. And we were in
